THE ANNIE W. (Circuit Court of Appeals, Second Circuit. February 4, 1924.) No. 220. Foley & Martin, of New York City (William J. Martin and George V. A. McCloskey, both of New York City, of counsel), for appellant. Macklin, Brown & Yan Wyck, of New York City (Horace L. Cheyney, of New York City, of counsel), for appellee.

Before HOUGH, MANTON, and MAYEB, Circuit Judges.

PEE OUEIAM.

Decree (297 Fed. 633) affirmed, with costs.
